What you need to know:

For the last one week, Ingwe fans have been flocking the merchandise shop to buy replica jerseys ahead of the new seasonClub members have been buying the replica jerseys at Sh2,600 through their branches while registered members buying directly from the shop part with Sh2,800The 35-year-old former Gor Mahia striker however warned Leopards to be careful so that cartels and unscrupulous business men don't hijack the whole process and leave the club in massive loses